---
title: Duck Breast with Pad Thai-Style Noodles
description: Packed full of fresh veggies with rich and zesty Asian-inspired flavours, our duck pad thai is super easy to whip up on a busy weeknight.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/duck-breast-5f6919f6-31c8cf0e.jpg
